{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:03.161Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/435\n\n## Problem\n`--json` output serializes every field including nulls and empty containers: `pm list --json` always emits a 23-key all-null `filters` echo (+ empty `runtime_filters`); `pm context --json` echoes `order/deadline/assignee/parent: null` per item. Measured: list 2552 B (TOON) vs 3773 B JSON (+48%); context 4582 vs 7034 (+53%). AGENTS.md already warns agents off `--json` for loops — the structured format is too expensive for the agents that need it.\n\n## Proposed fix\nLean JSON mode (`--json --lean`, `PM_JSON_LEAN=1`, or config key) that omits null values, empty arrays/objects, and collapses `filters` to only keys actually set (TOON parity). Verbose form stays as explicit opt-in.\n\n## Definition of done\nLean mode on list/get/context/search JSON paths; measured >=40% size cut on list+context in a tag-heavy tracker; contracts + docs updated; spec pins the null-omission rules."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-cfed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-435: lean JSON output mode omitting null/empty fields (~50% token cut for --json)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-435: --json is ~50% larger than TOON because it serializes all-null filters echoes and empty containers; add a lean JSON mode. Duplicate check: searched lean json/omit null/compact output — only MCP compact defaults (closed 2026-05-20) and mutation compactness (GH-437 item) matched; no open overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","gh-issue","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:03.161Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:03.161Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":180},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Lean JSON mode ships on list/get/context/search; null/empty omission rules pinned by spec; >=40% measured size cut on list+context in this workspace; docs+contracts updated"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"7770b1e9d53b6431e943cea54ff886e86520840ea69174fec9c1eb799d758842","message":""}
